quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  39,1,"Gafã sigbã yii Wẽnd nengẽ sẽn yaa wilb Naabã n yaa bʋʋd Mitã."
  39,2,"Tõnd sika gafã n tʋg fo nengẽ ne sɩda, bɩ f tũ Wẽnd tɩ f yaa sẽn yɩlg dĩinã ne-A."
  39,3,"Pa Wẽnd la dĩin yɩleng soab sɩda? La neb nins sẽn gãd lall-n-taas tɩ pa yɩ ne-A wã yetame: ""tõnd pa tũud-b rẽnda b na tall tõnd n pẽneg Wẽnde, pẽnegr sẽn yɩɩde"". Ad Wẽnd bʋʋda bãmb ne taab sʋka, bũmb ning pʋgẽ bãmb sẽn yõs taabã. Ad Wẽnd pa kãndgd ned ning sẽn yaa zĩrimbe-ned n yaa kɩfr ye."
  39,4,"La tɩ Wẽnd sã n da rat n na n yãk biiga, a na tũusẽ a sẽn naandã pʋgẽ A sẽn rate, yɩlgr be ne-A, Yẽnda la Wẽnd sẽn ya-a a Yembr n ya Modgdã."
  39,5,"A naana saasã la tẽngã ne sɩda, A kẽesda yʋngã wĩntoogã pʋgẽ, la a kẽesd wĩntoogã yʋngã pʋgẽ, la A nom wĩndgã ne kiuugã, b yembr kam fãa zoetame n na n tãag wakat sẽn yãk raare, ad Yẽnda la wilb Naab n yaa Yaafda."
  39,6,"A naana yãmb n yi yõ-yεng pʋgẽ, rẽ poorẽ n naan a pʋgẽ a pagã, la A sik kõbg a nĩi n kõ yãmba rũmsẽ wã. A naanda yãmb y ma-rãmbã pʋsẽ, naaneg toor-toor ligs a tãab pʋgẽ. Yãmb Wẽn-kãng la yãmb Soabã, Yẽ n so naamã, soab kae tɩ pa Yẽ ye; la yaa wãn tɩ b gõdg yãmba?"
  39,7,"Yãmb sã n kɩfle, ad Wẽnd sεk a Meng n yi yãmba, la A pa yard kɩflmã ne A yembsã ye. Y sã n pʋʋs barka, rẽ la A yard ne-a. Zɩ-tʋkd fãa pa na n tʋk a to zɩɩb ye. Rẽ poorẽ yãmb lεbeng zĩig yaa y Soabẽ wã t'A kõ yã bũmb ning y sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã kɩbare, ad A yaa Mit ne sẽn be yãadẽ."
  39,8,"La keelem sã n paam ninsaala, a boonda a Soabã t'a yaa sẽn lebs a mengã A nengẽ, rẽ poorẽ A sã n lebg n kõ-a neema sẽn yi A nengẽ (Wẽnd ) a yĩmda bũmb ning a sẽn da yɩ boond pĩndã. La a maan wõnesem-taas ne Wẽnd sẽn na yɩl n menes (nebã) n yi A sorã, yeele: ""wʋm noog ne f kɩfendã bilf bal tɩ ad fo yaa Bugum neda""."
  39,9,"La ned ning sẽn yãs ne tũudum yʋng wakatse n yaa suguud maanda, n yaa yasda, n yaeesd laahrã la a tẽed a Soabã yolsgo, yeele: ""rẽ yĩnga neb sẽn mi-bã makda ne sẽn pa mi-bã?"". Ad yaa yam bεεlã rãmb n tagsd n getẽ."
  39,10,"Yeele: ""yaa yãmb m yembs nins sẽn kõ sɩda, zoe-y Soabã, yel-sõmb be ne neb nins sẽn maneg dũni kãngã pʋgã; la Wẽnd tẽngã yalmame, ad b pidsda sugrã-rãmb b keoor tɩ pa yɩ ne geelg ye""."
  39,11,"Yeele: ""ad maam, b sagl-m lame tɩ m tũ Wẽnde, tɩ m yaa sẽn yɩlg dĩinã ne-A,"
  39,12,"B leb n sagla maam tɩ m yɩ lɩslaambã rẽenem""."
  39,13,"Yeele: ""ad mam yaeesdame tɩ m sã n kɩɩs m Soabã, ra-kãsengã raar naongo''."
  39,14,"Yeele: ""Wẽnd la mam tũuda tɩ m ya sẽn yɩlgd m dĩinã ne-A."
  39,15,"Bɩ y tũ bũmb ning yãmb sẽn rat tɩ pa Yẽnda. Yeele: ""ad bõndbã yaa neb nins sẽn bõn b mens la b zags-rãmb dũni yikr raarã, ad rẽnda la bõn vẽenega."
  39,16,"B tara b zugẽ wã Bugum pala, la tẽngrã me pal n be beenẽ, yaa rẽ la Wẽnd bugsd ne A yembsã: ""Mam yembsã! bɩ y zoe Maam""."
  39,17,"La neb nins sẽn zãag b mensã ne rʋbsã n pa rat n tũ-bã, la b lebs b mens Wẽnd nengẽ wã, sũ-noog be ne bãmba, bɩ f noog M yembsã sũuri."
  39,18,"Neb nins sẽn kelgd-b gomdã n tũud a sẽn yɩɩd sõmblemã, bãmb rãmb la neb nins Wẽnd sẽn kãnde, la bãmb rãmb la yam bεεl rãmba."
  39,19,"Ned ning namsg koεεg sẽn sɩdg-a soab zugu, rẽ yĩnga fo tõe n põsg sẽn be-a Bugum pʋga?"
  39,20,"La neb nins sẽn zoe b Soabã, bãmb rãmbã tara rot tɩ b yĩngrã me be rot sẽn me, tɩ ko-sood zoet b tẽngre. Yaa Wẽnd pʋlengo, Wẽnd pas yigdg pʋleng ye."
  39,21,"Fo pa yã tɩ Wẽnd sika koom sẽn yi saagẽ wã, t'a kẽes-a ko-ninẽ tẽngã pʋga, rẽ poorẽ t'a yiis kood t'a kõbgã yaa toor-toore, rẽ poorẽ t'a zelge, tɩ fo ne-a t'a yaa kõodre, rẽ poorẽ t'a maan-a t'a yaa sẽn zendge, ad be rẽ pʋgẽ, tẽegr ne yam bεεl rãmba."
  39,22,"Rẽ yĩnga ned ning Wẽnd sẽn pak a yãoog ne lɩslaoong tɩ yẽ be nuura pʋgẽ sẽn yi a Soabẽ wã? Rẽnd wɩɩbd be ne sũy sẽn kʋɩ-b n yi Wẽnd yʋʋr tẽegre, bãmb rãmbã bee meneng sẽn vẽneg pʋgẽ."
  39,23,"Wẽnd sika goam sẽn yɩɩd sõmblem, t'a (Aaya sãnda) wõnd taab n yɩlembdẽ, tɩ neb nins sẽn yaeesd b Soabã yĩn-gãnd sidgdẽ. Rẽ poorẽ tɩ b yĩn-gãndã la b sũyã yõgendẽ n tʋg Wẽnd yʋʋr tẽegre. Wãndã yaa Wẽnd kãndgr t'A kãndgd A sẽn rat-a soaba, la Wẽnd sẽn menemesd-a soab pa tar kandgd ye."
  39,24,"Rẽ yĩnga ned ning sẽn gũus a neng ne naon-wẽnga dũni wã yikr raarã, ɑ wõndɑ wɑlɑ b sẽn na n yeel wẽgdbã: ""lemb-y bũmb ning yãmb sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã""."
  39,25,"Neb nins sẽn reng bãmb taoorã yagsame, tɩ naongã wa-b zĩig ning b sẽn pa tẽede."
  39,26,"Tɩ Wẽnd kɩt tɩ b lem yãnd dũni vɩɩmã pʋgẽ, la laahr naongã n yɩɩd bedrem, tɩ b sã n ra yɩ n miime."
  39,27,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka, Tõnd wẽe bilgri ne nebã Alkʋrãan-kãngã pʋga, bilgr buud fãa, sãnd-sãnde bãmb na tẽege."
  39,28,"Alkʋrãan sẽn yaa laarabiindu, sẽn pa tar goalma, sãnd-sãnde b na zoe Wẽnde."
  39,29,"Wẽnd rɩka bilgr ne yemb-raoogo zu-soaben-dãmb sẽn zabd taab a poorẽ, la rao (a to ), ra-yεng sẽn so-a, rẽ yĩnga bilgr pʋgẽ b wõnda taaba? Pẽgr be ne Wẽnde, pa woto ye, b wʋsg fãa pa mi ye."
  39,30,"Ad fo (Mʋhammad) yaa kiida, la ad bãmb me yaa kiidba."
  39,31,"Rẽ poorẽ, yikrã raare y Soabã nengẽ la y na n bʋ ne taaba."
  39,32,"Ãnd wẽgd n yɩɩd ned ning sẽn yag Wẽnd zugu, la a yags sɩdã a sẽn wa n wa a nengẽ ? Rẽ yĩnga ka Gεhannem pʋgẽ n yaa gãag zĩig ne kɩfr-rãmbã?"
  39,33,"La neb nins sẽn wa-a ne sɩdã, la sẽn sɩdg-a sɩdã, bãmb rãmba la Wẽnd zoetba."
  39,34,"Bee b Soabã nengẽ b yĩnga b sẽn tʋll bũmb ninga, woto la manegdbã rolbo."
  39,35,"Bʋɩl yĩng tɩ Wẽnd na yaaf-ba, wẽng ninga b sẽn tʋmã, la A rol-b b keoorã, sõmblem sẽn yɩɩd bũmb ning bãmb sẽn tʋmã."
  39,36,"Rẽ yĩnga Wẽnd pa sek A yamba? La b yaeesd ne foom bũn-zẽms sẽn pa Yẽ, la Wẽnd sẽn menes-a soab pa le tar ned sẽn na n kãnd-a ye."
  39,37,"Wẽnd sẽn kãndg-a soab pa le tar menemsd ye, rẽ yĩngɑ Wẽnd pa wilb Naab n yaa maan n roalg Soab sɩda?"
  39,38,"La fo sã n sok-ba: ãnd n naan saasã la tẽngã b na yeele: ""yaa Wẽnde"". Yeele: ""yãmb yãame, bũmb ning yãmb sẽn boond tɩ pa Wẽndã, Wẽnd sã n rat maam ne naongo, rẽ yĩnga bãmb yaa naongã pãrgdb bɩ? Ma A sã n rat maam ne yolsgo, rẽ yĩnga bãmb yaa A yolsgã yõkd bɩ?"" Yeel: ""Wẽnd seka maam, Yẽ la bobl-m-mens rãmbã bobl ne-ɑ"""
  39,39,"Yeele: ""yaa mam neba! tʋm-y y sẽn tõe tɩ mam yaa tʋmda, la y na wa n bãnge""."
  39,40,"Ned nĩng naong sẽn wat-a soab nengẽ n nĩngd-a yãnde, la a sik a zug naon-duumdga."
  39,41,"Ad Tõnd sika gafã fo zug nebã yĩng ne sɩda, la ned ning sẽn kãnd-a yaa a meng yĩnga, ned ning sẽn menem-a me, rẽnd a menesda a menga, la fo pa boabld b zug ye."
  39,42,"Wẽnd n kʋʋd yõyã b kũumã wakato, la sẽn pa ki-b b gõeem wakat me, t'A yõk a sẽn bʋ kũumã a soab zugã, la A bas a to wã n tʋg wakat sẽn yãk raare, ad yel-soalem be rẽ pʋgẽ ne neb sẽn tagsd n getẽ."
  39,43,"Bɩ b gãda sugsdb tɩ pa yɩ Wẽnde? Yeele: ""ba tɩ b sã n yɩɩme n pa so bɑɑ fʋɩ, la b pa tar yam?""."
  39,44,"Yeele: ""ad sugsg fãa yaa Wẽnd n so, Yẽ n so saas la tẽng naam, rẽ poorẽ yaa Yẽ nengẽ la y na n lebe""."
  39,45,"La b sã n tẽeg Wẽnd a yembr yelle, la neb nins sẽn pa kõ sɩd ne laahrã sũy sẽn yikdi, la b sã n tẽeg rũbsã b sẽn tũud tɩ pa Yẽ wã, la b sẽn noogd b sũuri."
  39,46,"Yeele: ""yaa m Soaba! Saas la tẽng Yẽbgda, yel-soaandi la sẽn vẽneg mita, Foom n bʋʋd F yembsã ne taab sʋka b sẽn da yɩ n yõsd taab bũmb nins zugu""."
  39,47,"La ba tɩ neb nins sẽn wẽg-bã sã n tar bũmb ning sẽn be tẽngã pʋg gilli, la rẽ bilgri n lagem-a, b na n yao ne-a n fãag b menga n yi naon-wẽngã dũni wã yikr raare, tɩ vẽneg ne bãmb Wẽnd nengẽ, bũmb ning bãmb sẽn da pa yɩ n tẽedã."
  39,48,"Tɩ vẽneg ne bãmb bũmb ning b sẽn tʋmã wẽnga; tɩ sig bãmb zugu, bũmb ning bãmb sẽn da yɩ n yaandẽ wã."
  39,49,"La keelem sã n paam ninsaala a boonda Tõndo, rẽ poorẽ, Tõnd sã n tedg-a ne neema sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ la a sẽn yete: ""ad b kõ-a-la maam m bãngr yĩnga"". Pa woto ye, ad a yaa zarbgo, la ad b wʋsg fãa pa mi ye."
  39,50,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka, sẽn reng-b bãmb taoorã ra yeel-a lame, la pa naf bãmba bũmb ning bãmb sẽn da yɩ n paamdẽ wã ye."
  39,51,"Tɩ paam bãmb bũmb ning b sẽn tʋmã wẽnga. Neb nins sẽn wẽgd-b bãmbã pʋgẽ wã (b sẽn tʋm a Mohammad neb nins nengẽ wã) me na n paama bũmb ning b sẽn tʋmã wẽnga, la bãmb pa põsdb ye."
  39,52,"Rẽ yĩnga, b ka mi tɩ yaa Wẽnd n yεdgd rɩtlã n kõt A sẽn rat a soaba, la A yõbgdẽ? Ad bee woto pʋgẽ, tagmas-rãmb ne neb sẽn kõt sɩda."
  39,53,"Yeele: ""Mam yembs nins sẽn maan n zʋʋg b mens zugu! ra wãag-y tẽeb ne Wẽnd yolsgã ye, ad Wẽnd yaafda zunuubã zãnga, ad Yẽnda la yaafg Naab n yaa yoalsda""."
  39,54,"La y lebg n tʋg y Soabã nengẽ, la y sak n tũ-A, taoor tɩ naongã nan pa wa yãmb nengẽ ye, rẽ poore b pa sõngd-y ye."
  39,55,"La y tũ sẽn yɩɩd sõamã n ya bũmb ning b sẽn sik n kõ yãmb n yi y Soabã nengẽ wã, taoor tɩ naongã nan pa wa yãmb nengẽ ne lingri, tɩ yãmb pa tẽed ye."
  39,56,"Mɑɑne rẽ, tɩ yõor ra wa yeele: ""yaa mam nims ne bũmb ning mam sẽn maan kʋɩɩng Wẽnd wεεngẽ, la m da yɩɩme n lagem yaandba''."
  39,57,"Ma a yeele: ""Wẽnd sã n da kãndgẽ maam, m naan n zĩndẽ wẽn-zoetbẽ wã""."
  39,58,"Ma a yeel a sẽn wat n yã naongã: ""m sã n da tõe n lebgẽ lame, m paam n zĩndẽ manegdbẽ wã,(pɑ são)?""."
  39,59,"Yaa woto, sɩd la hakɩɩka Mam Aayayã ra waa fo nengẽ tɩ fo yags-ba, la f waoog f mengɑ, la f ra yɩɩme n yɑɑ kɩfre."
  39,60,"La dũni wã yikr raare, foo nee neb nins sẽn yag n roglg Wẽndã tɩ b nemsã sobge. Rẽ yĩnga pa Gεhannam pʋg n yaa gãag zĩig ne waoog-m-meng rãmba?"
  39,61,"La Wẽnd fãagda neb nins sẽn zoe-b Wẽndã, ne bãmb sẽn paam pʋɩɩrrã t'ɑ kẽes-b ɑrzẽnã, wẽngã pa sɩɩsd bãmb ye, bãmb pa sãamd b sũur me."
  39,62,"Wẽnd la bũmbã fãa naanda, Yẽ me la bũmb fãa bobl a meng ne-A."
  39,63,"A soo saas la tẽng kʋɩlen-biisi, la neb nins sẽn kɩfl ne Wẽnd Aaya rãmbã, bãmb rãmb la bõn-rãmba."
  39,64,"Yeele: ""Rẽ yinga zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnde la yãmb sagend maam tɩ m tũ, yaa yãmb a zɩtba?"""
  39,65,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka b tʋmsame tɩ wa fo nengẽ la neb nins sẽn reng fo taoorã nengẽ: ""tɩ fo sã n maan lagem-n-taare, hakɩɩka fo tʋʋmdã na lʋɩ, la f na lagem bõn rãmba""."
  39,66,"Bɩ f tũ Wẽnd la f lagem bark pʋʋsdbã."
  39,67,"Lɑ lɑgem-n-tɑɑrã rãmb pa zɩsg Wẽnd A zɩsgr tεkẽ ye, tɩ tẽngã fãa gill yaa A yõng-vuka yikrã raare, tɩ saasã yaa sẽn põd ne A rɩtgo, yɩlgem be ne Wẽnd, A naam leb n zẽkame n yi bũmb ning b sẽn maan ne-A lagem-n-taarã."
  39,68,"Tɩ b peeb Baorgã, tɩ sẽn be saasẽ la tẽngẽ fãa ki, rẽnda Wẽnd sẽn tʋll-a soaba, rẽ poorẽ tɩ b le peeb peebg a to tɩ bãmb yaa sẽn yik n yas n getẽ."
  39,69,"Tɩ tẽngã pɩl ne a Soabã nuura, tɩ b rɩgl Gafã, la b wa ne nabiyaam-rãmbã la sεεtbã, tɩ b bʋ bãmb ne taab sʋk ne sɩda, b pa na n wẽgd-b ye."
  39,70,"La b pids n kõ yõor fãa a sẽn tʋme, la Yẽnda (Wẽnde) n yɩɩd minim ne bũmb ning b sẽn tʋmdã."
  39,71,"La b kãag neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã zãma-zãma n tʋg Gεhannem, hal tɩ b sã n wa ta-a, b pakda a rag-noyã, t'a gũudbã yeel-ba: ""Rẽ yĩnga tẽn-tʋʋm-rãmbã pa wa yãmb nengẽ sẽn yi yãmb pʋgẽ n karemd yãmb y Soabã Aayay la b bugsd yãmb ra-kãngã sεgbã?"" La b yet tɩ yaa sɩda, la yɑɑ namsg koεεg n sɩdg kɩfr-dãmb zugu."
  39,72,"Tɩ b yeel: ""kẽ-y Gεhannem rag-noyã tɩ y yaa ruumdb a pʋgẽ, rẽnd waoog-m-meng zĩndig zĩig yɩ wẽnga""."
  39,73,"La b peeg neb nins sẽn zoe b Soabã zãma-zãma n tʋg arzãna, hal tɩ b sã n wa ta-a tɩ b pak a rag-noyã t'a gũudbã yeel-ba: Tɩlgr be ne-yã, y yɩlg yã, bɩ y kẽ-y-yã-a tɩ y yaa ruumdba""."
  39,74,"Tɩ b yeele: ""pẽgr be ne Wẽnd ningã sẽn sɩdg-a tõnd A pʋlengã la A kõ tõnd tẽngã tɩ yaa faado, tɩ d zĩ arzãnẽ wã d sẽn ratẽ; ad tʋmdb keoor be neema""."
  39,75,"Tɩ fo ne Malεgsã tɩ b gũbg Al-arsã, n yɩlg ne b Soabã pẽgre, tɩ B bʋ bõn-nɑɑnsã ne taab sʋk ne sɩda, tɩ b yeel: ""Pẽgr be ne Wẽnd sẽn ya bõn-naandsã Soabã""."
